Package net.runelite.api

Interface ParamHolder

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ItemComposition, NPCComposition, ObjectComposition, StructComposition
    public interface ParamHolder
    A composition that can hold `param` keys. This lets Jagex attach arbitrary constant data to certain items, objects, npcs, or structs for use in cs2
    See Also:
